<blockquote>Q: What is the difference between service and hospitality?</blockquote><blockquote>A: Service is black and white; service is color.</blockquote>

<strong>Black and white</strong> means you're doing your job with competence and efficiency. <strong>Color</strong> means you make people feel great about the job you're doing for them.




<strong>[book:Unreasonable Hospitality|60018618]</strong> is on the <strong>Short List</strong> of four <strong><a href="https://beantownweb.blogspot.com/2023/08/best-business-books-2022.html" target="_blank">Best Business Books of 2022</a>.</strong>

